POSITION OVERVIEW\par
=================\par
We are seeking an exceptional Data Scientist to join our world-class engineering organization and drive \par
the next generation of technological breakthroughs. This role offers the unique opportunity to work \par
on large-scale distributed systems, cutting-edge AI/ML applications, and cloud-native architectures \par
that directly impact millions of users globally.\par
\par
As a Data Scientist at Apple, you will be at the center of our most strategic initiatives, collaborating \par
with product managers, designers, data scientists, and fellow engineers to deliver solutions that \par
define industry standards. You will have the autonomy to make architectural decisions, influence \par
our technical roadmap, and mentor the next generation of engineering talent.\par
\par
This position is ideal for a seasoned professional who thrives in ambiguous environments, has a \par
passion for solving complex problems at scale, and wants to make a meaningful impact on the future \par
of technology. You will be working with technologies like Kubernetes, Apache Kafka, TensorFlow, \par
React, microservices, and cloud platforms across AWS, Azure, and GCP.\par
